prompt.behavior_examples:
例1: 阻断完整记录 LLMGateAuditor.record_gate_block( session_id="s-001", trace_id="t-abc", action_type="challenge", llm_payload={"statement": "这是一个很长的内容..."}, gate_result={"decision": "BLOCK", "gate": "L2"}, alignment_report={"dropped_fields": [], "filled_slots": {}, "valid": True}, safety_report={"triggered_phrases": []}, ) → _logs[0] = { "session_id": "s-001", "trace_id": "t-abc", "timestamp": "2026-05-05T12:00:00Z", "action_type": "challenge", "llm_payload_truncated": '{"statement": "这是一个很长的内容..."...truncated', "gate_result": {"decision": "BLOCK", "gate": "L2"}, "alignment_report": {...}, "safety_report": {...}, }
例2: 按门禁统计 _logs = [block(L2), block(L2), block(Safety)] count_blocked_by_gate() → {"L2": 2, "Safety": 1}
例3: 空 payload record_gate_block(llm_payload=None, ...) → llm_payload_truncated = ""
